la la la la la... im bored... and wow... i had ntohing to do... so i was thinking to myself "im gunna write in that there live journal oh mine!" lol... jk... but... yeah... i juss felt like writting in this... cuz i have nothing better to do... so yeah... this is gunna be a pretty boring entry... im juss gunna talk about that there day oh mine... lol... about my day.. so yeah... i got up... and i started getting ready for skool... and my mom needed to take a shower... so i stoped doing my make up... AND I HAD ONE EYE DONE! and i left the bathroom... so she could shower... wen she got out the shower... i started doing my makeup again... and brushing my teeth... and my mom came in again... and shes like "are you done yet?" and she didnt have to be at work til 8!! and she was rushing me so she could get ready... man... so yeah... i went in my room and finished getting ready by my mirror... man... then i went outside... and it was FUKIN FREEZING MAN!!! and i went to my bus stop... and i stood there... la la la.... while i was freezing my ass off (not that i really have an ass)... and then... the bus came... i got on the bus... sat in the same seat i sit in every morning... with Greg... the lil nerdy kid who trys to be everyones friends... and pays ppl to be his friend... lol... and then... we got to skool... and i walked into skool... put my bookbag down by where i normaly stand... and noticed my friend (tanya) wasnt there... so like... i like... saw kristen (11 toed... cross eyed LOSER) and asked her if tanya was on the bus... and she said she wasnt... so i hung out with kristen... and we saw this dude shawn she knew... and i always saw this dude in the halls n stuff.... (he has the cutest lil gf) and i didnt think KRISTEN could actually be friends with him... man... i was like.. WTF?! UR FRIENDS WITH HIM!? and yeah... we left him alone cuz his gf came... and yeah... we didnt wanna bother them... ya no? so then... like... i went bak to where i stand... and i talked to willard... hes like... my friend from bio class... and i takled to him for a while... then he left... so i went n talked to kyle and adam... and like... then the 5 min bell rang... so i went to English... and like... la la la... sat there... listened to the teacher talk about w/e the fuk she was talking about... then the bell rang... i went to study hall... talked to ppl... n shit... then sat there for a long while... doing nothing... and then i like... startewd writting poems... kinda got kinda sad/deppressed... so yeah... thennnn... the bell rang... me n sara walked to our bio classes (not the same class as eachother) and i was in bio... la la la... we had a sub... he gave us time to work on our packets that were due... we took a vocab test... then basically talked the rest of the time... then to algebra i went! and a counsler lady came to talk to us about like... what alectives we wanted to be in next year n shit... (i wanna be in german and some type of art or photography) and then i went to child development... and like... learned about mothers n what they shouldnt do wen there pregnant... and what could happen if they do something wrong... and blah blah blah... then i went to lunch... hung out with friends... went to the study part of lunch... la la la... then i went to gym... didnt change for gym... cuz its swimming.. and its that time of the month... so yeah... i cant swim... and yeah... then i went outside... and went to say bye to like... my friends n shit... went to look for my bus... found my bus... came home... la la la... did NOTHING AT ALL!!! and now im here... writting what i did for today... and now... im writting... and writting... and writting... and i would keep doing this... but ppl r talking to me on AIM so ima go... cuz its hard trying to ttype on here and to friends... so yeah... :)

A and F!!! wtf!? aero? man... those r fukin preppy man... and she fukin hated the fact that i called her a prep... she said "i dont act like those bitchy preps" and me n johanna kinda became friends again... and kassy still hated me... well... kassy IMed me online one night... and we were talking... and kinda became "friends" and we were nice to eachother for about 2 weeks maybe... but then Kassy heard that i called her a prep behind her bak... which i fukin didnt! and then was bein a bitch again... and sooo... she hated me again... and all my friends and i... would talk shit about her at the lunch tabel... and vivian... man... she was funny.... she fukin called kassy white trash (CUZ SHE WAS) and i juss... thought that was so funny man... wow... vivian was the best... wow... hah... wow... some of my friends go to skool with Kassy and Johanna... man... i feel sorry for them... wow... well... ne wayz... me n johanna were friends again... and i went to a fest thing with her... and like... we saw kassy... and kassy didnt wanna hang with johanna wen she was with me... and i didnt wanna hang with kassy ne ways.. so amelia was with kassy... and sara and some other chicks... and they left kassy to hang with johanna and me... and so... we went to meet up with carolyn (BIGGEST POSER ON EARTH) and then... like... they were all saying how kassy was gunna show up... JOHANNAS LOOKING FOR U! and blah blah blah... and i'd keep walking... and like... johanna found gillespie (a sk8er dude who i used to be friends with and she was like... BEST friends with) and started to look for me... and this shit was funny... cuz... man... i had fun without them... and they found me... and johanna was on the fone... yelling and screaming to her aunt... and i was walkign... and they were following me... and im fukin stubern man... and then... we yelled and yelled... and johanna called some dude a nigger... and he wanted to kill her... and yeah... and blah blah blah... and... umm... well... we were going bak to johannas aunts car... and i see kassy... she yells... "kay... think what u wanna" and so blah blah blah... me n johanna kinda like... totaly stoped being friends... we were friends during the summer kinda... hung out for like... 1 month of the summer... she was takling shit about kassy... butt kassy didnt know... umm... we kinda stoped hanging and she became friends with kassy again... and... stoped being friends with me now...
